Made up conversation in the present tense
by Mr.Paper » Wed 07.29.2009 11:00 pm At a restaurant.Waiter: konnichiwaClient: konnichiwaWaiter: kyo wa nani o hoshii kaClient: hai, ehhh, ikutsuka no sushi o hoshii. kudasai.Waiter: kyo wa sushi o sugoi desu neeClient: a so desu ka, sugoi!Translation:Hello!Hello.What do you want today?Yes, ummm, some sushi, pleaseTodays sushi is amazing!Really? Great!
Mr.Paper
Posts: 59Joined: Wed 07.29.2009 9:46 pmLocation: Illinois
Native language: Spanish
