Re: Made up conversation in the present tense
by Mr.Paper » Thu 07.30.2009 5:17 pm Kyo wa sushi o sugoi desu yoToday's (particle) sushi (particle) amazing is.Wa indicates that today's is the topic of the sentence. Desu is a verb (to be) refering to sushi, the direct object, so the particle "o" is used.Today's sushi is amzing.
